<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="yes" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="nominative">who himself</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 is a key figure of the Italian Renaissance and a central figure of its political component, most widely known for 
<REF ID="1673.3" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="subj-det">
